  <brief_title>Effects of Scalp Nerve Blocks on Systemic Inflammation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Scalp Nerve Blocks on Systemic Inflammation After Meningeoma Resection Surgery：a Prospective Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
